      <title>随着债券空头的抱怨，从 Pimco 到 DWS 等投资者纷纷准备逢低买入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/as-bond-bears-grumble-pimco-t-rowe-and-dws-gear-up-to-buy-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员对今年债券收益率的痛苦上涨感到惊讶，但鉴于他们持续假设美国经济最终将在 2024 年放缓，他们仍在寻求抢购美国债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-03/as-bond-bears-grumble-pimco-t-rowe-and-dws-gear-up-to-buy-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Mar 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
